underlying_goal: To understand why V5.x sandbagging prompt results were excluded from a presentation in favor of V4.1 results.
primary_success: Synthesizing findings from multiple .md files to explain that V5.x prompts were excluded because they either didn't actually sandbag or the experiments used the wrong detector.
brief_summary: The user asked why V5.x prompt results were missing from slides. Claude investigated internal documents and explained that the V5.x experiments were either flawed or showed that the prompts didn't work as intended, justifying the focus on the more compelling V4.1 results.
